article_title: Hospital says dozens killed in central Gaza.
sentence: At  least  45  people  have  been  killed  in  central  Gaza,  the  spokesperson  for  the  al-Aqsa  hospital  in  Deir  al-Balah  has  told  the  BBC,  after  reports  of  an  Israeli  airstrike  in  the  city.
